18 $\\times\n10^{11}$ $M_{\\odot}$ for any kind of CDM dark-matter halo profiles, under the\nassumption that stars and gas do not influence the predicted dark matter\ndistribution in the MW. This methodological paper encourages the use of the\nEinasto profile for characterizing rotation curves with the aim of evaluating\ntheir total masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Jul 2021 11:13:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Jul 2021 19:50:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2021 14:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
